Non-Contentious Construction Associate 3+PQE, Abu Dhabi
Non-Contentious Construction Associate 3+PQE, Abu Dhabi
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
This well established and highly regarded global law firm is currently recruiting for a non-contentious construction associate to join their top tier team in Abu Dhabi.
The ideal candidate will be 3+PQE and have excellent training and solid construction experience from a highly regarded UK or International law firm. GCC experience is preferred, but not essential – strong lawyers from the UK, Australia or New Zealand will be considered.
The team advises on the procurement of a wide range of assets across all major industry sectors, with a particular focus on oil & gas and major infrastructure projects throughout the Middle East. Clients include developers, funders and contractors.
For further details, candidates fulfilling the above criteria are invited to send their CV in complete confidence to
